<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
<main>
    <div class="track-cont">
        <div class="insights mini">
            <h2>Personalized Insights</h2>
            <p>Whoa! Your spending habits reveal that most of your expenses are going toward <span><%=mostSpentCategory %></span>. It looks like this category is taking the biggest bite out of your budget! Maybe it's time to rethink your priorities? ðŸ’°ðŸ“Š</p>
        </div>
        <div class="streak mini">
            <h2>Gamification & Streaks</h2>
            <p>You've logged expenses for <span><%=streak %><% if(streak > 1){ %> days<% }else{%> day<% } %></span> in a row! Keep going!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tips mini">
            <h2><%= title %></h2>
            <p><%= tip %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="graph">
            <h3>Graphical View</h3>
            <% if (locals.chartUrl){ %>
                <img src=<%=chartUrl %> alt="chart">
                <% } %>
                    <form action="/track" method="post">
                        <select name="type" id="type" required>
                            <option disabled selected>Select a category</option>
                            <option value="bar">Bar</option>
                            <option value="line">Line</option>
                            <option value="pie">Pie</option>
                            <option value="radar">Radar</option>
                        </select>
                        <button type="submit">Generate</button>
                    </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</main>
</html>